public class IdBasedUnionGraph

A graph implementation that wraps all named graphs of a named graph set and that uses the identifier-based query execution.

Constructor Detail

IdBasedUnionGraph

public IdBasedUnionGraph(List members,
                         NodeDictionary nodeDict)
Creates a union of the identifier-based graph implementations in the given list.

Parameters:
members - a list of IdBasedGraph objects (the parameter is not typed by intention because we initialize a base class list of Graph objects and the compiler would bark even if an IdBasedGraph is a Graph)
nodeDict - the node dictionary used to get identifiers for RDF nodes that occur in triple pattern queries issued to this graph (graphBaseFind(com.hp.hpl.jena.graph.TripleMatch))
